  "description": "The signified (*signifié*) is one half of [Saussure](../../../../../../humanities/domains/general/domains/people/ferdinand-de-saussure.md)'s dyadic model of the [sign](./sign.md). It is the concept evoked by the [signifier](./signifier.md) — not a referent in the world but a mental concept within a language system.",
